00050 static void exec(void *data, bNode *node, bNodeStack **in, bNodeStack **out)
00051 {
00052     if (in[0]->data) {
00053         if (node->id) {
00054             MovieClip *clip= (MovieClip *)node->id;
00055             CompBuf *cbuf= typecheck_compbuf(in[0]->data, CB_RGBA);
00056             CompBuf *stackbuf= alloc_compbuf(cbuf->x, cbuf->y, CB_RGBA, 0);
00057             ImBuf *ibuf;
00058 
00059             ibuf= IMB_allocImBuf(cbuf->x, cbuf->y, 32, 0);
00060 
00061             if (ibuf) {
00062                 RenderData *rd= data;
00063                 ImBuf *obuf;
00064                 MovieTracking *tracking= &clip->tracking;
00065                 int width, height;
00066                 float overscan= 0.0f;
00067                 MovieClipUser user= {0};
00068 
00069                 BKE_movieclip_user_set_frame(&user, rd->cfra);
00070 
00071                 ibuf->rect_float= cbuf->rect;
00072 
00073                 BKE_movieclip_get_size(clip, &user, &width, &height);
00074 
00075                 if (!node->storage)
00076                     node->storage= BKE_tracking_distortion_create();
00077 
00078                 if (node->custom1==0)
00079                     obuf= BKE_tracking_distortion_exec(node->storage, tracking, ibuf, width, height, overscan, 1);
00080                 else
00081                     obuf= BKE_tracking_distortion_exec(node->storage, tracking, ibuf, width, height, overscan, 0);
00082 
00083                 stackbuf->rect= obuf->rect_float;
00084                 stackbuf->malloc= 1;
00085 
00086                 obuf->mall&= ~IB_rectfloat;
00087                 obuf->rect_float= NULL;
00088 
00089                 IMB_freeImBuf(ibuf);
00090                 IMB_freeImBuf(obuf);
00091             }
00092 
00093             /* pass on output and free */
00094             out[0]->data= stackbuf;
00095 
00096             if (cbuf!=in[0]->data)
00097                 free_compbuf(cbuf);
00098         }
00099         else {
00100             CompBuf *cbuf= in[0]->data;
00101             CompBuf *stackbuf= pass_on_compbuf(cbuf);
00102 
00103             out[0]->data= stackbuf;
00104         }
00105     }
00106 }

00131 {
00132     static bNodeType ntype;
